{"tid":1692382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Ｖ煞蛋糕被DQ  賽會改口：裝飾過大","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:27:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f53b885f9238609dda0443239feeb614b1582ff","tid":1692382,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/ZWE2ZGU7DJV4VGZOLZ7AI56GB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FZWE2ZGU7DJV4VGZOLZ7AI56GB4%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=ace7df2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FZWE2ZGU7DJV4VGZOLZ7AI56GB4%2F&h=3c06fe6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/ZWE2ZGU7DJV4VGZOLZ7AI56GB4/</a><br />\n<br />\nＶ煞蛋糕被DQ <br />\n賽會改口：裝飾過大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/jJs8gneQl8YQgcoNJs1FXG-0RqI=/802x996/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/2SLSMU3R76PDF52FDNVLCMGZAQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FjJs8gneQl8YQgcoNJs1FXG-0RqI%3D%2F802x996%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F2SLSMU3R76PDF52FDNVLCMGZAQ.gif&h=270c4298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本地餐飲店3rd Space製作充滿香港抗爭主題的蛋糕，在英國參加一連三日的國際蛋糕節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港人抗爭屢成國際新聞，有香港蛋糕師以本港示威作主題，製作蛋糕遠赴英國參加「國際蛋糕節2019」，卻敵不過具玻璃心的內地選手，向主辦方篤灰指「港獨滲透比賽」等，作品終因「具冒犯性」而被DQ。主辦方辯稱，蛋糕被DQ是由於蛋糕裝飾過大，違反賽規。<br />\n<br />\n記者：張雅婷<br />\n<br />\n一連三日的「國際蛋糕節2019」曲終人散，以班戟為主打的本地餐飲店3rd Space派員參賽，作品為一個三層蛋糕。蛋糕以香港抗爭者為造型，包括「V煞面具」、雨傘及戴安全頭盔的示威者等，頂部為黑膠唱片機造型，轉盤上轉着黑色香港特區區旗。底座則是仿照連儂牆，貼上「香港人加油」、「We are Hongkonger」等便利貼。作品介紹寫着譴責港府和港警察，亦有提及「光復香港，時代革命」等。<br />\n<br />\n3rd Space向《蘋果》轉述參賽的蛋糕師指，蛋糕長、闊、高各60厘米，從香港帶到英國後，竟損毀了六成，在酒店修補了五日。帶到會場期間，更遇上滂沱大雨，掉失了八個裝飾公仔，只剩一個可完整展示。雖然失去獎項，但對她而言，卻是人生最好的經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地參賽者抹黑「港獨」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：立場記者被扣手銬拘捕<br />\n<br />\n作品早於前日就被內地參賽者陳瑤投訴，她在微博稱有關作品宣傳港獨，而「在中國選手們團結一致共同努力下」，有關蛋糕終被撤展。她更理直氣壯說：「世上沒有絕對的自由，建立在法律，在國家利益不受侵犯的前提之下的才叫自由。」<br />\n<br />\n3rd Space則在fb及IG公佈消息，展示由主辦方發出的電郵，被DQ的原因是由於蛋糕具冒犯性（offensive），但未有具體解釋具冒犯性的地方。3rd Space表明不會屈服：「我們覺得不忿和憤怒，但我們仍然會做自己，會上訴會爭取，即使最後結果不能盡如人意，但我們仍會用多一口氣告訴你，你錯了。」3rd Space又用簡體字寫：「不要用一頂『港獨』的帽子去抹殺了解事情的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n面對主辦方「跪低」，網民都為本港參加者抱不平，到大會的Twitter及fb炮轟。主辦方事隔一日於fb承認收到有人對蛋糕的投訴，但DQ的原因是蛋糕裝飾和超出可容許的範圍，違反賽規，又堅稱此決定不涉政治，此說法與給3rd Space的「具冒犯性」解釋明顯不符。網民亦不收貨，在留言展出其他具大型裝飾的蛋糕，質問為何DQ標準不一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/6_BENY03qfn2E7KFy6YXa3opdK4=/802x514/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/YGHESLVPVCZYJ4EFHJGOUYEELA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F6_BENY03qfn2E7KFy6YXa3opdK4%3D%2F802x514%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FYGHESLVPVCZYJ4EFHJGOUYEELA.gif&h=f074938a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比賽中有其他巨型且涉政治意味的蛋糕。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/MuH4Gx9IuhmPYHwlE8ttdRaikQY=/802x426/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/DNZT7KI7KTQFIVEHT5D3LXO5C4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FMuH4Gx9IuhmPYHwlE8ttdRaikQY%3D%2F802x426%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FDNZT7KI7KTQFIVEHT5D3LXO5C4.gif&h=5be91880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地人陳瑤（圓圖）篤灰後，V煞蛋糕被DQ消失。<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"11fb9af64b6896bec452ce546d54a6bc94f8b38c","tid":1692382,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"DQ 出名，英國幫到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f06e75a16828925239233a1e1b56496641a4423","tid":1692382,"uid":14897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"果條仆街咩樣蛋糕"},{"pid":"053eabe23e3fefd6a3f91b1a784dc33695a0364a","tid":1692382,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"多謝共不落帝國"},{"pid":"af35b9c36e89d3ead86c36fe45e4e18580651000","tid":1692382,"uid":127410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f06e75a16828925239233a1e1b56496641a4423","tid":1692382,"uid":14897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"果條仆街咩樣蛋糕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}